Title: Provides for the payment of state aid to the town of Ashford, in the county of Cattaraugus, for state land therein
Summary: Provides for the payment of state aid to the town of Ashford, in the county of Cattaraugus, for state lands in such town.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public lands law, in relation to the payment of state aid on account of certain state lands in the town of Ashford, in the county of Cattaraugus
